# Agent Logging Rule

At the end of each task, log the different agents used for that task to the console by running a terminal command.

Run `echo` (or equivalent) to output an "Agents used" summary to the terminal, listing:
- Any MCP tools called (e.g. Codacy, Supabase, Figma)
- Any subagents launched via mcp_task (e.g. explore, shell, code-reviewer)
- Other specialized tools or agents invoked during the task

Example: `echo "[Task complete] Agents used: codacy_cli_analyze"`
